body: I had an improv thing at school last night and we had these workshops with experienced improvisers or comedians, it was lots of fun. One of them was called Dan somethingorother and when he got up in front of the room to introduce himself, he did this weird wave thing and went, “Hello, my name is (pause) Dan”. I just about fell out of my chair.
